+### Error Handling and Recovery
+```javascript
+class RobustPlanner extends GOAPAgent {
+  async handlePlanningFailure(error, context) {
+    switch (error.type) {
+      case 'MATRIX_SINGULAR':
+        return await this.regularizeMatrix(context.matrix);
